    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏的Q&amp;A</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Q：游戏需要全程联网吗？没有朋友可以玩吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A：游戏有单人模式，也可以和好友组队，或匹配其他玩家一起出战。想要找伙伴一起组队，可以加入官方群。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果想彻底断网离线游玩，可以在标题界面点击右上方的存档图标，在选择存档界面点击按钮进入离线模式。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Q：游戏后续会更新更多内容吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A：会的！我们目前在全力优化游戏的性能表现和战斗体验，并修复目前发现的问题。不久之后将会有大版本更新，之后还会加入新角色、新关卡、新的Boss。敬请期待！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Q：我在游戏中遇到一些问题，或一些Bug，该怎么办？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A：如果您在游戏中发现Bug，或一些影响体验的问题，请发送邮件到 <a href=\"mailto:support@mojugames.com\">support@mojugames.com</a> ，或在社区与我们联系，我们会及时帮您解决。我们力求为每一位玩家都提供最完善的服务和最好的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特别提醒：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>如果您在中国境内访问亚洲服务器联机游戏时出现卡顿或掉线情况，请关闭加速器或任何代理软件/VPN。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/4fd1ca95bb3f183c897e90038fb6d47b.avif?t=1729238511\" width=600 height=94 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/8dae338bc31e40085fc88e935f0b582b.poster.avif?t=1729238511\" width=604 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/8dae338bc31e40085fc88e935f0b582b.webm?t=1729238511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/8dae338bc31e40085fc88e935f0b582b.mp4?t=1729238511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>4个不同战斗风格的角色：实力均衡的刀盾、远程射击的弓箭手、爆发力惊人的巨剑以及灵巧迅捷的刺客。每个角色都有自己独特的攻击方式和特殊技能，并具有丰富的动作元素如闪避、格挡和弹反。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/027ee056e867aeeba52c537feaf8ff3e.avif?t=1729238511\" width=600 height=94 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/2a172bbd55f70970a0a8a49185e5993a.poster.avif?t=1729238511\" width=604 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/2a172bbd55f70970a0a8a49185e5993a.webm?t=1729238511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/2a172bbd55f70970a0a8a49185e5993a.mp4?t=1729238511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>特色的五行能力系统，分为金木水火土五种属性。每种属性之间具有相生相克关系，玩家可以搭配这些能力组合，形成各种独特的战斗流派。此外，数百种效果各异的铭文为战斗增添更多变数。一些铭文会带有负面效果，玩家在选择它们需要一定的策略。但搭配不同效果的铭文可能会有出其不意的效果。除此之外，游戏中还可以获得改变攻击形式的武器印记，配合五行能力与铭文，给玩家更多探索空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/a6ebc84770228b2e112cc76792fc0f70.avif?t=1729238511\" width=600 height=94 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/46944109f441aa57455548bdb1d15e62.poster.avif?t=1729238511\" width=604 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/46944109f441aa57455548bdb1d15e62.webm?t=1729238511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/46944109f441aa57455548bdb1d15e62.mp4?t=1729238511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>游戏最多支持4人在线合作。玩家可以组队冒险，或与随机玩家匹配组队。游戏中还提供了联机专属的随机任务和道具，让联机战斗更为欢乐有趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/1f5fc0ad7762809eae0dc2c6e9197aeb.avif?t=1729238511\" width=600 height=94 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/a5934bdfbfb8d8e5c38de42e9da71c40.poster.avif?t=1729238511\" width=604 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/a5934bdfbfb8d8e5c38de42e9da71c40.webm?t=1729238511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/extras/a5934bdfbfb8d8e5c38de42e9da71c40.mp4?t=1729238511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>解锁新角色，升级能力、属性与天赋。超过300多种能力、铭文、道具和武器印记，以及丰富的角色成长系统。玩家可以在不断挑战中解锁各种强化功能，让下次战斗更为轻松爽快。游戏中还有大量自定义皮肤饰品，让角色变得与众不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>目前版本游戏内容：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4个玩家角色（之后会更新更多！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13个关卡，包括至少36个随机生成的地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过10个Boss和各种不同的敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >300多种能力、符文、道具和武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的可解锁内容和大量自定义皮肤</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们会持续更新更多！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如想了解更多内容，请加入我们的官方QQ群：727232923</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并请关注我们的B站官方帐号：</p>",
